{"tid":1856354,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［大發現］荔景紀律部隊宿舍收埋大量csi口罩","createTime":"2020-02-01T14:43:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-01T15:13:39.000Z","uid":99313,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d5170fcd7bf3a931e3934a7042c93a3aae31bbc2","tid":1856354,"uid":99313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T14:43:14.000Z","msg":"是咁的 呢幾日搭小巴 <br />\n聽到個大嬸係電話到同佢啲朋友講話叫佢地快啲上黎拎口罩 又話咩好多 仲以為邊個大媽搶左咁多口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點知佢原來住荔景紀律部隊宿舍 睇住佢係宿舍到落小巴再行入去 <br />\n有一日 搭小巴又見到宿舍果到一家大細上小巴 坐我前面 又比我望到佢地個袋入面有成盒csi口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請問大家可以點舉報宿舍入面既人 懷疑入面收埋左好多csi口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ab0f37d05ec9ac74ec7d8eff0d19e2599ff2906","tid":1856354,"uid":79181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T15:09:39.000Z","msg":"「罷工」港龍員工需要支持！請幫忙宣傳！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1856363\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1856363</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7bd361e37645549e6c9edddf1e4a2fce6456d9f4","tid":1856354,"uid":91833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T15:11:05.000Z","msg":"你又唔攞埋一份<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"030a629d753452000f33fc9e4f468bd516944ab5","tid":1856354,"uid":81140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T15:13:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}